title: Buenos Aires Rolls Out Blockchain-Based Digital ID for Storing Official Documents
description: According to The Block, the Buenos Aires city government is launching a blockchain-based digital ID service named QuarkID. This service aims to securely store official documents such as marriage and death certificates. title: VanEck to donate 10% of ETF profits to Ethereum contributors
description: Global asset management company VanEck has promised to give the Ethereum Protocol Guild 10% of its Ethereum Futures ETF profits for the next ten years.

title: SEC hustles to delay Bitcoin ETFs amid looming government shutdown
description: The SEC delayed decisions on proposed spot Bitcoin ETFs from VanEck, WisdomTree and Fidelity — all filed on Sept. 28.
